{"tid":1416788,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武過後，文宣大方向","createTime":"2019-08-05T15:34:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T16:30:16.000Z","uid":267454,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2419e17fc48c4d5bc7e56af5bbfcb75ca7937fa2","tid":1416788,"uid":267454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:34:16.000Z","msg":"從今日既777/警方/政府跨部門記者會，可以知道：<br />\n<br />\n1. 政府多次強調<span style=\"color: red;\">政府已經作出回應，但示威者唔收貨</span> 好不負責任但佢的確不停loop<br />\n<br />\n2. 政府想spin去港獨同民生<br />\n<br />\n3. 警方迴避所有關放執法既問題，唔駛旨意係佢度聽到認錯<br />\n<br />\n4. 跨部門會係一面倒講有乜影響，幾微小都要提，造成示威者無理既感覺<br />\n<br />\n所以，希望文宣運作集中呢幾個方向<br />\n<br />\n方向一：係勇武之前有幾多和理非表達方式做過，但政府無理到<br />\n一般而言，6.9，6.16，烈士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最多人提<br />\n但其實真係仲有好多次和理非表達，如陳伯絕食，大律師公會遊行，香港總商會提出過建議，連儂牆等<br />\n作用：首先，數哂出黎，令勇武再做其他行動出師有名<br />\n其次，政府日日話要和平理性，仲話佢已經回應左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span style=\"color: red;\">但其實唔聽既根本就係政府</span><br />\n<br />\n方向二：改口號<br />\nSorry我依一刻搵唔返d po，但「五大訴求，缺一不可」「光復香港，反黑反暴」都ok<br />\n但777提左我地，佢要spin去港獨<br />\n今次運動既進步，<span style=\"color: red;\">就係由舉手和平左膠示威，進化去勇武都接受到</span>，但主因係6.12既警方濫用暴力，令好多人覺得真係接受唔到<br />\n你可能覺得，屌咁都係進步？得嗰雞碎咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但呢樣真係需要時間，今次connect到二百萬人遊行，都係因為「反送中」而不是港獨<br />\n請大家真係要三思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n方向三：煲返所有不合理既野<br />\n講緊7.21元朗恐襲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，天水圍少女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，tear gas放題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，黑警講粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢d<br />\n最近資訊太多太複雜，講真我追住live都唔知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，立場叫有旁述，但now有線果d有時都無<br />\n好似今晚北角果度，一開始睇live只睇到爆破璃（好似係有線），後尾先見到屋入面個人拎住菜刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，再見到有人講返呢班人係北角白衫人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">資訊太多，好易沖淡一d重要議題，唔好旨意其他人自行整合資訊，有時係想都有心無力，可以既話要做埋俾佢地</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有區會，垃圾會要搞，收到建制一部份皮，唔好俾佢停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要幫到前線，文宣係和理非都做得到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望幫到文宣攞ideas<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3ddb4404c59c071ce05856433608ac1018deb0","tid":1416788,"uid":267454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:34:50.000Z","msg":"希望幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7005b4189dc467c85721002fd1542f7a8cc0794e","tid":1416788,"uid":267454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:35:37.000Z","msg":"廢p牌整圖都唔識希望幫到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed36992fdbbb79094ab43090404e408d7a61146a","tid":1416788,"uid":267454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:38:17.000Z","msg":"希望幫到手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dc739c7f75fbd88edb6a9a2787e49c1c1ff0609","tid":1416788,"uid":267454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:41:27.000Z","msg":"要Connect最多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9675afeef9a394315b5955673cc1039c44c706f1","tid":1416788,"uid":9583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:43:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f815e5be5f1a055453b6f6af745ea7379b435182","tid":1416788,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:44:21.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"1135349efad2fa221e40aa81d81c2c1de99d6472","tid":1416788,"